# megaman

## megaman 1

### weakenes

guts -> cut -> elec -> ice -> fire -> bomb

guts 2nd: hyper bomb
cut 2nd: fire storm

- yellow devil: thunder beam
- copy robot: fire storm
- CWU-01P (bubbles): super arm (use only after the 3rd one)
- willy machine 1: fire storm, rolling cutters
